<br>
I am English, (and not an anti-war protester btw, though i am afraid that i do believe the motivation is primarily oil, and i also think the war is obscenely wasteful and could have been avoided.)<br>
<br>
I also like Americans, (always have.) In this country you grow up watching a lot of American TV, but you know what one of the nicest experiences in life is (imho<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    ). Meeting a real American and finding that they're not like the ones on TV!<br>
<br>
